Package: org.jlab.analysis

[Groovy] Class ExtendedConstants

      • org.jlab.analysis.ExtendedConstants 
      • @groovy.transform.CompileStatic
class ExtendedConstants
extends Constants

        Sets the Lund pid to particle mass/charge/name hashmaps and other analysis constants. As you might expect the pid to mass hashmap is somewhat more extensive.

        Version:
        1.0
        Authors:
        Matthew McEneaney
